name: Englewood Cosmetology Trades
tag_list: trade-school, hair-salon, nail-salon, facial-spa, beauty-salon, beauty-school, barber-school, barber-shop
overview:
If you are a licensed Cosmetologist or Hairstylist and want to get more training to get your Colorado Barbers License, check out our new Barbering Plus Programs.

Our goal at Englewood Cosmetology Trades is to assist students in discovering their own abilities to succeed as artistic, ethical, skillful hair professionals in today’s fashions and trends with goals of their own in their chosen field of cosmetology trades.
